source.name: Completed EO 12866 Regulatory Reviews by Calendar Year
source.description: Annual data set of draft rules reviewed by OMB under Executive Orders 12291 and 12866.  The data provide information by agency, length of review in days, and economic significance.  This data set provides annual data going back to 1981.
